[src:bob-ferguson-infielder/1871-in-baseball] The tenth founding member, the National club of Washington, did not enter a team for the championship until 1872.
[src:bob-ferguson-infielder/1872-in-baseball] The following are the baseball events of the year 1872 throughout the world.
